original_title: Thong Ngin Fan Ngin Jit Jong
overview: Thong Ngin Fan Ngin Jit Jong is a local wisdom in the form of a philosophy of unity inherent in the Bangka Belitung Islands. This film tells about the close relationship between ethnic Chinese and Malays wrapped in the philosophy of Thong Ngin Fan Ngin Jit Jong.
title: Thong Ngin Fan Ngin Jit Jong
